title: #187 - I'm Over Trisha Paytas & Papa John Calls In
description: On this episode of The H3 Podcast the gang return to talk about all the drama that's gone down over the past two weeks- SomeOrdinaryGamers, Trisha & Moses, and various other dweebs. Then we are joined by the god-Papa himself to bring you a very special announcement... Papa bless!
